OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 30 APR
OL,4,CMISCELLANEOUS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1964FTelevision sets manufactured as
OL,7,Fof this date are required to be
OL,8,Fequipped to receive UHF channels.
OL,9,
OL,10,CG1980FToday is the first day of a
OL,11,Fsiege in the Iranian Embassy.
OL,12,
OL,13,FTwo BBC TV News employees, who were
OL,14,Fgetting press accreditation, were
OL,15,Famongst those held hostage.
OL,16,
OL,17,FChris Cramer (news organiser) was
OL,18,Freleased after 2 days due to illness,
OL,19,Fwhilst Sim Harris (sound recordist) was
OL,20,Fheld until the siege ended.
